# INTRO
##################################################
intro:
  heading: Transform Your Property with Custom Masonry & Hardscaping
  paragraphs:
    - >
      Hardscaping includes the permanent features that give your landscape structure, beauty, and functionality. Patios, walkways, retaining walls, outdoor kitchens, fireplaces, fire pits, pool decks, stone stairways, and decorative masonry all work together to create outdoor living spaces that are attractive, durable, and easy to enjoy for many years.
    - >
      At S. Phaneuf & Associates, we design and build custom masonry and hardscape projects throughout Massachusetts. Every project is planned around your property, your lifestyle, and the way you want to use your outdoor space. Whether you're creating a quiet backyard retreat or a complete entertainment area, we build outdoor environments that feel like a natural extension of your home.
    - >
      Our experienced craftsmen work with premium materials including bluestone, granite, natural stone, brick, and concrete pavers to construct patios, walkways, retaining walls, outdoor kitchens, fireplaces, pool decks, and complete outdoor living spaces. Every installation is customized to complement your home's architecture and surrounding landscape.
    - >
      Beautiful hardscaping begins long before the first stone is installed. Proper excavation, grading, drainage, and base preparation are essential to the long-term performance of every project. By building a solid foundation first, we help prevent settling, drainage problems, and premature repairs caused by New England's changing seasons.
    - >
      Beyond improving curb appeal, professionally built hardscapes create additional living space for relaxing, entertaining, outdoor dining, and spending time with family and friends. Features like retaining walls can also solve grading problems, while patios and walkways make your property safer and easier to navigate.
    - >
      Every homeowner has different goals. Some want a welcoming front entrance with custom stone steps and walkways, while others dream of a backyard complete with a pool patio, outdoor kitchen, fireplace, and fire pit. Our design process focuses on creating solutions that fit your property, budget, and long-term vision.
    - >
      Whether you're replacing an aging patio, expanding your outdoor living area, building around an existing swimming pool, or planning a complete landscape transformation, our team manages every phase of the project from design through construction with attention to detail and quality craftsmanship.
  callout:
    title: Built for Massachusetts Homes
    text: >
      Every masonry and hardscape project is constructed using proper base preparation, drainage, and proven installation techniques that help withstand Massachusetts' freeze-thaw cycles while providing decades of beauty, durability, and reliable performance.
  closing: >
    Browse the featured projects below to see how we've helped homeowners throughout Massachusetts transform ordinary backyards into beautiful outdoor living spaces with custom patios, retaining walls, fireplaces, outdoor kitchens, pool decks, walkways, and decorative masonry designed to be enjoyed for years to come.


